{{POV|time=2020-05-17T15:50:55+00:00}}{{Original research}}{{not|民族主义}}{{Redirect|爱国|偶尔被简称为“爱国”的国家|爱尔兰}} 
{{模板:Nationalism}} 
'''爱国主义'''是一种对[[国家|国家]]和家园的[[依恋|依恋]]感，并与具有相同情感的其他[[公民|公民]]结盟。这种依恋可以是与自己的[[祖国|祖国]]有关的许多不同感受的结合，包括[[种族|种族]]，文化，政治或历史方面。它包含了一系列与民族主义密切相关的概念，但并不等同于民族主义。<ref name="books.google.com">{{cite book |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=5N-wqTXwiU0C&pg=PA313 |title= Historical Dictionary of the Enlightenment |author= Harvey Chisick |date= 2005-02-10 |accessdate= 2013-11-03 |isbn= 9780810865488 |archive-date= 2014-09-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140925183305/http://books.google.com/books?id=5N-wqTXwiU0C&pg=PA313 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/nationalism/ |title= Nationalism (Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy) |publisher= Plato.stanford.edu |date=  |accessdate= 2013-11-03 |archive-date= 2018-09-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180922061455/https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/nationalism/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/patriotism/ |title= Patriotism (Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy) |publisher= Plato.stanford.edu |date=  |accessdate= 2013-11-03 |archive-date= 2018-06-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180611140503/https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/patriotism/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>

==历史流變==
